name: Seated Dumbbell Curl
title: While there is more core engagement for bicep curls standing, this isn't usually the goal for bicep training.

name: Seated Cable Row
title: During the seated row, the primary movers are the lats and rhomboids.

name: Hammer Curl
title: Hammer curls target the long head of the bicep as well as the brachialis.

name: Standing Leg Curl
title: The standing hamstring curl is a bodyweight exercise that tones your hamstring muscles.

name: Lateral Raises
title: A lateral raise works your shoulder muscles as well as your triceps.

name: Hack Squat
title: The hack squat involves standing on the plate, leaning back onto the pads at an angle.
